# Webhook Receiver — {{tool_name}}

> Tier 4: vendor pushes events; receiver must be built and exposed at
> a stable URL. The build session implements an HTTP endpoint that
> verifies signatures, deduplicates events, and feeds them into the
> agent's inbox.

